| `src/layers/presentation.fl:29` | `(handler, request: HttpRequest) → Result<HttpResponse, _>` 패턴 |

## 구현할 파일 (3개)

### 1. `src/api/server.fl` (400줄)
```
struct SemanticSearchServer
  hybridSystem: HybridIndexSystem
  config: ServerConfig    # host, port, corsEnabled

struct ServerConfig
  host: string
  port: number
  corsEnabled: boolean
  maxBodySize: number     # 기본 1MB

fn newSemanticSearchServer(config) → SemanticSearchServer
fn startServer(server) → Result<unit, string>
fn routeRequest(server, request) → Result<HttpResponse, string>
fn buildCorsHeaders() → map<string, string>
fn buildJsonResponse(status, body) → HttpResponse
fn buildErrorResponse(status, message) → HttpResponse
```

### 2. `src/api/handlers.fl` (300줄)
```
# 5개 핸들러

fn handleInsert(server, request)
  # POST /api/v1/insert
  # body: { "text": "...", "metadata": {} }
  # → { "id": "doc_xxx", "status": "inserted" }

fn handleBatchInsert(server, request)
  # POST /api/v1/insert/batch
  # body: { "texts": ["...", "..."] }
  # → { "count": 5, "status": "ok" }

fn handleSearch(server, request)
  # POST /api/v1/search
  # body: { "query": "...", "k": 10 }
  # → { "results": [...], "count": 10, "time_ms": 0.054 }

fn handleSearchByVector(server, request)
  # POST /api/v1/search/vector
  # body: { "vector": [...128 floats...], "k": 10 }
  # → { "results": [...], "count": 10, "time_ms": 0.054 }

fn handleStats(server, request)
  # GET /api/v1/stats
  # → { "total_docs": 1234, "mode": "hybrid", "avg_search_ms": 0.054 }

fn handleHealth(server, request)
  # GET /api/v1/health
  # → { "status": "ok", "version": "1.0.0" }
```

